title: Baby Cora drawing
---
author: Roni Kobrosly
---
body:

This one took quite a while. The reference is one of my favorite pics of her as a baby. I learned and tried a trick with this, which proved to be pretty effective. You take the reference face and break it up, via a ruler, into quadrants. It makes nailing the proportions so much easier. 


